    <item>
      <title>澳门博彩收入低于预期，经济进一步放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/macau-gaming-revenue-misses-estimate-in-further-sign-of-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳门 1 月份博彩收入下降 5.6%，低于分析师预期，并进一步表明中国疲软的消费信心正在拖累这个世界最大博彩中心的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/macau-gaming-revenue-misses-estimate-in-further-sign-of-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 05:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
